s beaten DSS-1 more than once over the three rounds, giving\nit the best comparative rating among the participants.\n  By design DSS-1 performs consistently, that is, identical problem setup is\nguaranteed to yield identical decisions. The study showed that only two experts\nmanaged to demonstrate partial consistency within a tolerance but ended up with\nmuch lower scores.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 May 2020 17:42:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 2020 10:58:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-05"}
