reated a new Python package selectionfunctions\n(https://github.com/gaiaverse/selectionfunctions) which provides easy access to\nour selection functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 May 2020 18:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-12"}
