mber, respectively. We\ndemonstrate that both OAM and AP uncertainties are two monotonic functions of\n{\\delta} and two various distribution types of OAM spectrum and image intensity\nin this singular light with identically equivalent PGs. We experimentally\ngenerate these singular light beams.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 May 2020 07:43:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jul 2020 07:49:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Aug 2020 10:38:44 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 1 Dec 2020 08:35:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-02"}
