 tested on the IRIS dataset which exhibits $\\approx46\\times$\nmore energy efficient per MAC (multiply and accumulate) operation compared to\nearlier classifiers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 May 2020 15:36:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-20"}
